==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Polymorphosis
<hw>Pol`y*mor*pho"sis</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[NL. See
<er>Poly-</er>, and <er>Morphosis</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<def>The assumption of several structural forms without a corresponding
difference in function; -- said of sponges, etc.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Polymorphous</ent>⟦br⟧
